OL,6,FChildren who contract the disease can
OL,7,Fbecome very unwell. It can lead to
OL,8,Fhospitalisation and even death in some
OL,9,Frare cases.
OL,11,FAn outbreak was declared after it
OL,12,Flinked all four cases "through
OL,13,Fattendance at a healthcare setting on
OL,14,F21 March".
OL,16,FPHW is identifying contacts of the
OL,17,Fcases, and is providing their parents
OL,18,Fwith advice on what action to take and
OL,19,Finformation about the signs and
OL,20,Fsymptoms of measles.
