OL,3,CMeasles outbreak declared in Gwent as
OL,4,Ctwo new cases confirmed
OL,6,FIt added that both patients are
OL,7,Freceiving appropriate care.
OL,9,FBeverley Griggs, consultant in health
OL,10,Fprotection for Public Health Wales and
OL,11,FChair of the multi-agency outbreak
OL,12,Fcontrol team, said: "Measles is a
OL,13,Fhighly infectious disease, and cases
OL,14,Fhave been rising across the UK and
OL,15,FEurope in recent months, so this
OL,16,Fdevelopment is not unexpected.
OL,18,F"As a result of having clear evidence
OL,19,Fof spread from the initial case, we
OL,20,Fhave declared an outbreak of measles
OL,21,Fin the Gwent area.
