OL,6,F"We are identifying contacts of all
OL,7,Fcases and will contact them to provide
OL,8,Fadvice on symptoms and what action to
OL,9,Ftake if they need to seek medical
OL,10,Fadvice. Where contacts are
OL,11,Funimmunised, we will also request
OL,12,Fwithdrawal from nursery, education or
OL,13,Fother high risk settings. This is a
OL,14,Froutine public health action to help
OL,15,Fprevent further cases of measles in
OL,16,Fthose who are most at risk.
