OL,7,Fit is really important that you
OL,8,Ftelephone before arrival, or
OL,9,Fimmediately notify staff on arrival at
OL,10,Fyour GP surgery or other healthcare
OL,11,Fsetting, so they can be promptly
OL,12,Fisolated and avoid any further
OL,13,Ftransmission.""
OL,15,FMeasles can be prevented by the highly
